<p>
<p>
lo all,
<p>
I just wanted to say what a good idea sorc wars are.
<p>
I love them, and the wizzes that let us have impromptu sorcerizings when we
ask for them :-)
<p>
Sorc wars are a great way to learn inter-persona combat (quite different
from fighting mobiles I think you'll agree) without risking your favorite
sorc/necro/whatever. A necessary survival skill or a right old laugh,
depending on your point of view, learning how to look after yourself is one
of the best skills you can acquire in MUD. One day I might be able to take
my high-lives out and have a decent set without being hacked to pieces by
"someone" in the first ten minutes...
<p>
So lets have more and more sorc wars also how about team sorc wars, wizzes
v. mortals that sort of thing? They're great fun.
<p>
Jadeporl the increasingly bloodthirsty.
